snippet.title: 「Gotcha Racing Second 」promotional video
snippet.description:
Try on Gacha and challenge on the racing!

There are infinite combinations of parts!


The Gacha-Customizing Racing Game,
"Gotcha Racing Second"
has given a new look on Nintendo Switch!

Repeat racing and rolling gacha, and aim to be a Grand Prix winner!


Title : Gotcha Racing 2nd
Genre : Gacha-Customize Racing Game
Release Date : March 29th, 2018
Price : $ 9.99 / € 9.99
ESRB : EVERYONE
No. of Players : 1 player for online
1-4 players for offline
Platform : Nintendo Switch™


Gotcha Racing Second Official Website
http://www.arcsystemworks.jp/arcstyle/gacharacing2nd/

ARC SYSTEM WORKS OFFICIAL WEBSITE
http://www.arcsystemworks.jp/
